* Best Practices for\nTables and Views
** Managed tables preferred
***_ Better Unity Catalog integration
***_ Automatic optimization
***_ Simpler lifecycle management
** Views: keep queries focused
***_ Avoid too many layers
***_ Document purpose and audience
** Dynamic views for security
***_ Centralize security logic
***_ Reduce data redundancy
** Standard vs materialized views
***_ Standard: fast queries or real-time data
***_ Materialized: complex aggregations
** Use liquid clustering
***_ CLUSTER BY instead of partitioning
***_ Auto-optimizes based on query patterns
@endmindmap
